**************
The problem requires finding \(P(A_1 \cup A_2 \cup A_3)\) using Theorem 1.1-6, which is the inclusion-exclusion principle for three events. The principle states:

\[
P(A_1 \cup A_2 \cup A_3) = P(A_1) + P(A_2) + P(A_3) - P(A_1 \cap A_2) - P(A_1 \cap A_3) - P(A_2 \cap A_3) + P(A_1 \cap A_2 \cap A_3)
\]

Given:
